import React from 'react'
import Home_left from '../home/home_left/HomeLeft'
import News from './News'
export default function NewsFeed() {
    return ( <
        div className = "row"
        style = {
            { paddingTop: '20px' } } >
        <
        Home_left > < /Home_left> <
        News / >
        <
        /div>
    )
}
